## Read order for AI agents
1. **`AGENTS.md`** — always-applied workspace rules (multi-tenant, API boundaries, fiscal guardrails, validation commands)
2. **`REGKASSE_AI_ONBOARDING.md`** — project brief for medium/large tasks
