## Quick reminders (non-exhaustive)
- POS UI: German (de-DE). Admin UI: i18n (de/en/tr). IDE explanations: Turkish.
- Cross-tenant access → HTTP 404 (not 403). Never bypass tenant query filters except Super Admin ops.
- POS uses `/api/pos/*`; Admin uses `/api/admin/*` — do not cross boundaries.
- High-risk: payments, TSE/RKSV chain, tenant isolation, FinanzOnline outbox, voucher ledger.

